The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | International | Hamilton, girlfriend split up
                                                                                                                           17                                                                                      Hamilton, girlfriend split up
                              Hamilton, Scherzinger                            
	London, Jan. 11: Lewis Hamilton and Pussycat Doll Nicole Scherzinger have split after two years, it has been announced.        
	The 25-year-old British racing driver and US pop star, 31, said they wanted to concentrate on their careers.        
	A joint statement from their spokesmen confirmed: Nicole Scherzinger and Lewis Hamilton can confirm that they have decided to go their separate ways.        
	The pair started dating after meeting at the MTV Europe Awards in Munich in November 2007.                     THE DAILY TELEGRAPH                                                                                                                                                   
